Class CruiseManager

java.lang.Object
  CruiseManager

public class CruiseManager
extends java.lang.Object

CruiseManager is the central piece of this collection. Both CruiseShipManagerCLI and CruiseShipManagerGUI run all actions through this class. From here commands get routed to the correct sub class. Actions like passenger removal start here and then are directed to the Cruise class, then the passengers class, and eventully down to the list containing the passengers themselves. CruiseManager utilizes a double linked list to keep track of all cruises in the system.
